## Embedding YouTube Videos

Videos are a powerful way to explain concepts. Use this format:

### Video Embedding Code

```html
<div class="video-container">
    <iframe 
        width="560" 
        height="315" 
        src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/VIDEO_ID" 
        title="Video Title"
        frameborder="0" 
        allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" 
        allowfullscreen>
    </iframe>
</div>
```

Or simpler syntax:
```html
<iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/VIDEO_ID_HERE"></iframe>
```

### Example Video (Replace with Your Video ID):

```html
<div class="video-container">
    <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/VIDEO_ID_HERE"></iframe>
</div>
```

*To find the video ID: Go to any YouTube video. The URL is `youtube.com/watch?v=VIDEO_ID`. Copy that ID into the iframe src.*

## Design Best Practices

### Color Palette

The website uses a sophisticated color scheme:

| Color | Use | Hex Code |
|-------|-----|----------|
| Primary | Buttons, Headings | #9C8FB0 |
| Secondary | Text | #333333 |
| Background | Page Background | #F5F5F5 |
| Accent | Highlights | #2196F3 |

### Typography

- **Headings:** Segoe UI, Bold
- **Body Text:** Segoe UI, Regular
- **Code:** Courier New, Monospace

### Spacing

Use consistent spacing:
- Margins: 20px, 30px, 40px
- Padding: 15px, 20px, 30px
- Line Height: 1.6 - 1.8

